{"tid":1166790,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"五二三地震求生教學（好似係）","createTime":"2019-05-22T16:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T16:08:12.000Z","uid":50366,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"efa4618f88e274bfcb9fc29ced13acf699d36b78","tid":1166790,"uid":50366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T16:08:12.000Z","msg":"五二三地震就到<br />\n一個求生教學post都無<br />\n我試下整個懶人速食包<br />\n<br />\n求生包執唔切，最重要有<br />\n水，乾糧零食，雨具，毛巾（保暖用），火機火柴蠟燭之類，證件，越簡單越輕便越就手就越好<br />\n其他就算啦，好似證書果類就收好佢<br />\n<br />\n震緊點攪，唔好蹲下，唔好（捐）枱底，搵大件硬淨野然後縮埋一舊（埃）埋去<br />\n<br />\n部份地震求生教學source<br />\n地震求生<br />\n<a href=\"https://frank727.pixnet.net/blog/post/30281751-%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E5%8D%81%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E6%95%91%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E4%B8%80%E5%91%BD~%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E6%B1%82%E7%94%9F%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffrank727.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F30281751-%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25B3%2587%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%2590%2598%25E6%2595%2591%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25B7%25B1%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2591%25BD~%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%259C%2587%25E6%25B1%2582%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25B3%2595&d=cCjVArjaL4JVgeQxTlbTSyEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=eb5cfe9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://frank727.pixnet.net/blog/post/30281751-%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E5%8D%81%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E6%95%91%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E4%B8%80%E5%91%BD~%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E6%B1%82%E7%94%9F%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95</a><br />\n求生包，自己google<br />\n<br />\n利申, 發夢見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}